weather-description =
    A weather widget for the FreeSynergy desktop powered by Open-Meteo.

    Shows current weather conditions (temperature, wind, precipitation, humidity)
    and a 5-day forecast for a configured location. Open-Meteo is a free, open
    weather API based on open-data weather models — no account or API key required.

weather-features =
    - Current conditions: temperature, wind, precipitation, humidity
    - 5-day forecast with daily highs and lows
    - Set location by city name or coordinates
    - Celsius and Fahrenheit support
    - Powered by Open-Meteo — no API key required
    - Weather icons adapt to the active desktop theme
